<plot>This documentary provides fans with a behind-the-scenes look at the making of this high-tension thriller about the decisions faced by a submarine crew who think the President may have ordered a missle launch. Includes interviews with stars Washington and Hackman, as well as other members of the cast and crew, who relate their experiences in working on the film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573840</url></doc>
